track_notes: From the free car park north west of Birches Corner walking a section of the Macmillan Way West long distance path. Great views from the summit of Lundy Island, Bristol Channel and South Wales on a clear day. Outward and return route shown, 2.6 miles round trip.

Total time (including ops): 1hr 20m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Wills Neck Circuit from Triscombe. Jun 2020.
